Flicker grabbed her, firmly but gently and looked into her eyes.

Flicker:  There is nothing about you that's ordinary, and I don't 
mean just your spark.  To be honest I have devoted my life to 2 other 
beings, Megatron and you, and I would give my life in a heartbeat for 
either one......my shuttle isn't much farther.

He continues on toward the shuttle.
